=================================
 Bkleaner - Book cleaner utility
=================================

Change stylesheets of ebooks in EPUB format.

Installation
============

To build a source distribution, one need `setuptools` then::

  python setup.py sdist

To install locally using Python::

  pip install dist/bkleaner-0.1.tar.gz --user

To uninstall::

  pip uninstall bkleaner

Dependancies
============

To create a source distribution, one need `setuptools`.

All dependancies can be found in the file `setup.py`. 

Whole code has been tested under Python 3.

